variable (K)

/-- The matrix that gives the representation on `stdBasis` of the image by `commMap` of an
element `x` of `(K ‚Üí+* ‚ÑÇ) ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ` fixed by the map `x_œÜ ‚Ü¶ conj x_(conjugate œÜ)`,
see `stdBasis_repr_eq_matrixToStdBasis_mul`. -/
